&lt;&#x2F;ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;flow-diagram&quot;&gt;Flow Diagram :&lt;a class=&quot;anchor&quot; aria-hidden=&quot;true&quot; href=&quot;#flow-diagram&quot; hidden=&quot;&quot;&gt;#&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;
