&lt;&#x2F;blockquote&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;1-client-requests-a-presigned-url-from-the-next-js-server&quot;&gt;1. Client requests a presigned URL from the Next.js server&lt;a class=&quot;anchor&quot; aria-hidden=&quot;true&quot; href=&quot;#1-client-requests-a-presigned-url-from-the-next-js-server&quot; hidden=&quot;&quot;&gt;#&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;
