&lt;h2 id=&quot;2-next-js-api-route-creates-a-presigned-url-using-aws-sdk&quot;&gt;2. Next.js API route creates a presigned URL using AWS SDK&lt;a class=&quot;anchor&quot; aria-hidden=&quot;true&quot; href=&quot;#2-next-js-api-route-creates-a-presigned-url-using-aws-sdk&quot; hidden=&quot;&quot;&gt;#&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;
